request.description:
Get a paginated list of the authenticated user's conversations.

Each conversation includes:
- **peer** — the other user's `id`, `name`, `avatarUrl`
- **lastMessage** — preview of the most recent message
- **unreadCount** — number of unread messages in this conversation

### Response
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Conversations fetched successfully",
  "data": {
    "items": [
      {
        "id": "conv-uuid",
        "peer": {
          "id": "user-uuid",
          "name": "John Doe",
          "avatarUrl": "https://..."
        },
        "lastMessage": {
          "id": "msg-uuid",
          "text": "Hey, I'll be there in 5 mins",
          "senderId": "user-uuid",
          "createdAt": "2026-02-15T10:30:00Z",
          "type": "TEXT"
        },
        "unreadCount": 2,
        "updatedAt": "2026-02-15T10:30:00Z"
      }
    ],
    "nextCursor": "conv-uuid-last",
    "hasMore": true
  }
}
```

